{"id":348729,"date":[{"year":1957,"month":6,"day":11}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"255","ytitle":"","mtitle":"林歌","ftitle":"香山旅札之一","authors":["唐湜"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐湜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，绿叶纷披的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树的海!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光从枝叶间筛下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如点点燃烧的金花!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我转过山坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝望着郁郁的山谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山的青翠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛在寂静里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄滴落。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪儿都是好客的树顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把把绿伞下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有红羽、翠羽的鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在欢唱金色的正午。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望不见它们的展翅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但它们的歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却给谷间的寂静更增加了分量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在喜悦的颤动里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众多的思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一阵花雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向我凝思的眼睛纷纷飘来!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我仿佛也是一颗树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风，水与阳光在我的心里忽然凝合成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个巨大的欢乐!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，祖国的树林在歌唱!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，祖国的树林在歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平的时辰!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也要加入这庄严的合唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高歌祖国的百花齐放!"}]}